Creating Groups 9

In this step we are going to create groups that we use them as slicer, chart and map since we have plenty of items in ‘Fine Category’, ‘Position’ and Teams and we can’t make our users have to scroll across to see the data.

Load the  grouped items for Conference, Position and Fine category from the above.

STEP 1. Click ‘Teams’ table

STEP 2. Select ‘Team’ column 

STEP 3. Click the eclipse (…) 

STEP 4. Click New group and  follow the attached gif to create group name called Conference. If you want to add more items in the group just Ctrl key + click the items that you want to add. Use the attached screenshot to create Conference group.

Download and Follow the above steps to create Fine Category and Position groups. 

NFL celebrated its 100 years in 2019. Through out these times, several changes were made to make the league very competitive and profitable. The idea of creating two conferences NFC  (National Football Conference and American Football Conference and played as one league started in 1970.  The champions from the tow conferences play for Super bowl champion.  It is believed that more than 140million people watch the super bowl in each season  throughout the world.
